Package: terrademo
Title: Demo of Using the Terra Package with Pixi Build
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Pixi", "Dev", email = "hi@prefix.dev", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A minimal example showing how to use the terra geospatial package
    with pixi-build-r. This demonstrates that pixi can resolve all system
    dependencies (GDAL, GEOS, PROJ) automatically via conda-forge.
License: MIT
Imports:
    terra
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
